DAMAGEDENTITY.description:
Triggers when the user damage an entity. 
The target entity will be set as the damaged entity

DAMAGEDBYENTITY.description:
Triggers when an entity damages the user. 
The target entity will be set as the damaging entity

DAMAGEDBYPROJECTILE.description:
Triggers when an entity damages the user. 
If the damaging entity is a projectile, the target entity will be set as the source of the projectile. 
Otherwise, The target entity will be set as the damaging entity

onlyProjectiles.description:
If true, will only trigger if the damaging entity is a projectile. 
Defaults to false

DAMAGEDENTITYWITHPROJECTILE.description:
Triggers when the user damages an entity directly or with a projectile. 
The target entity will be set as the damaged entity

onlyProjectiles.description:
If true, will only trigger if the damage is from a projectile. 
Defaults to false

LAUNCHPROJECTILE.description:
Triggers when the user launched a projectile. 
The target entity will be set as the launched projectile

PROJECTILEHIT.description:
Triggers when a projectile shot by the user landed and/or hits an entity. 
The target entity will be set as the projectile

DAMAGED.description: Triggers when the user gets damaged

causes.description: The causes of damage. Defaults to all damage causes

TOGGLEGLIDE.description: Triggers when the user glides or unglides

LOOP.description: Triggers periodically every couple of ticks

period.description:
The delay period in seconds (1 = 20 ticks). 
Defaults to 1

COMBAT.description:
Triggers when the user damages an entity or gets damaged by an entity. 
The target entity will be set as the damaged entity or the damaging entity respectively

DEATH.description:
Triggers when the user is killed. 
The target entity will be set as the killer if it exist

TARGET.description:
Triggers when the user targets an entity. 
The target entity will be set as the target

TARGETED.description:
Triggers when the user is targeted by an entity. 
The target entity will be set as the entity that targeted the user

VEHICLE.description:
Deprecated, use ENTERVEHICLE instead. 
Triggers when the user enters a vehicle. 
The target entity will be set as the vehicle

ENTERVEHICLE.description:
Triggers when the user enters a vehicle. 
The target entity will be set as the vehicle

BECOMEVEHICLE.description:
Triggers when an entity enters the user, thus using the user as a vehicle. 
The target entity will be set as the entering entity

EXITVEHICLE.description:
Triggers when the user exits a vehicle. 
The target entity will be set as the vehicle

PLAYERJOIN.description: Triggers when the user joins the server

PLAYERQUIT.description: Triggers when the user exits the server

If true, will only trigger if the damage is from a projectile. 
Defaults to false

TAME.description:
Triggers when the user tames an entity. 
The target entity will be set as the tamed entity

Triggers when the user equips an armour. 
The item will be set as the equiped item
